# Stack

- Use Next.js App Router
- Use TypeScript
- Use Tailwind CSS
- Use shadcn/ui
- Use Supabase for auth/database
- Use server components by default
- Use server actions when possible

# Architecture

- Frontend in Next.js
- AI processing in FastAPI
- Supabase for auth/storage/database
- Keep business logic in services
- Use modular architecture

# Code Style

- Keep files under 300 lines
- Use async/await
- Avoid any
- Add loading and error states
- Use functional React components only

# Instructions

- Always read the docs folder before generating code
- Follow architecture.md, database-schema.md and ai-pipeline.md
- Prefer server components
- Prefer server actions over API routes where possible

# UI

- Clean SaaS style
- Mobile responsive
- Accessible